caption: Limited Public Forum
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy1340(V)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Although permitting some commercial advertising and commercial promotion within the school system, the Board of Education does not intend to create a public forum or to open school property and/or facilities, including its electronic media, print publications, or school facilities, for unlimited access by outsiders or advertising by the general public.
